data.description: 'CURRENTLY UNDER CONTRACT, SELLER WILL CONSIDER BACKUP OFFERS' PERFECT BEACH HOUSE  Great Location,  LOW HOA $350 per year!  Welcome to the tranquil neighborhood of Lyndell Plantation in beautiful Panama City Beach, FL! Located south of HWY 98 (Back Beach Road), this stunning home offers a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and coastal charm. Nestled in a quiet beach community, this property is just minutes away from popular attractions such as Pier Park, County Pier, and the breathtaking beaches of Panama City Beach. Short term rentals are allowed in this neighborhood. So this house is ideal for a primary, vacation home or an investment property! It is only a 5 minute bike or golf cart ride to the beach access straight down Lyndell Lane. There is plenty of parking available at the end of Lyndell Lane or the nearby County Pier.Step into your very own Outdoor Paradise!!  This home boasts an inviting fenced-in backyard, Pool, Tiki Bar, outdoor cooking area complete with a covered grill, AND a hot tub for the cooler evenings! The garage is deeper than most allowing space for extra tools and  shelving provides extra storage.  Whether you want to relax poolside with a good book or host memorable gatherings with friends and family, this outdoor space has it all.  The roof is standing seam and inspected by roofing company who noted no issues or dings and ''solid''  after recent storms. This Lyndell Plantation home encompasses the essence of coastal living. With its thoughtfully designed layout and stylish finishes, it offers both comfort and functionality. From the open concept living areas that provide ample space for entertaining to the cozy bedrooms that offer a peaceful retreat, every aspect of this home has been carefully crafted with your lifestyle in mind.Come see this home today!
